item.title: Really annoying problem! plz help!
item.dc:creator: @Rictoo Rictoo
item.description:
@Rictoo wrote:

The problem is the Ground Java files’ Class Declarations aren’t public.
To make the Class Declarations Public do this:

Find the Ground Java file
To find the Ground Java you have to look through EVERY SINGLE JAVA FILE and find one which looks simaler(sp?) to this:

[code]
class Class19_Sub3 extends Class19
{

public Class19_Sub3(int i, int j, int k)
{
    anInt1397 = 9;
    aClass37Array1409 = new Class37[5];
    anIntArray1410 = new int[5];
    anInt1401 = anInt1398 = i;
    anInt1399 = j;
    anInt1400 = k;
}

public int anInt1397;
int anInt1398;
int anInt1399;
int anInt1400;
int anInt1401;
public Class13 aClass13_1402;
public Class45 aClass45_1403;
Class15 aClass15_1404;
Class9 aClass9_1405;
Class42 aClass42_1406;
Class24 aClass24_1407;
int anInt1408;
Class37 aClass37Array1409[];
int anIntArray1410[];
int anInt1411;
int anInt1412;
boolean aBoolean1413;
boolean aBoolean1414;
boolean aBoolean1415;
int anInt1416;
int anInt1417;
int anInt1418;
int anInt1419;
Class19_Sub3 aClass19_Sub3_1420;

}[/code]

Now to make the Class Declarations Public do this:

[code]
class Class19_Sub3 extends Class19
{

public Class19_Sub3(int i, int j, int k)
{
    anInt1397 = 9;
    aClass37Array1409 = new Class37[5];
    anIntArray1410 = new int[5];
    anInt1401 = anInt1398 = i;
    anInt1399 = j;
    anInt1400 = k;
}

public int anInt1397;
int anInt1398;
int anInt1399;
int anInt1400;
int anInt1401;
public Class13 aClass13_1402;
public Class45 aClass45_1403;
public Class15 aClass15_1404;
public Class9 aClass9_1405;
public Class42 aClass42_1406;
public Class24 aClass24_1407;
int anInt1408;
Class37 aClass37Array1409[];
int anIntArray1410[];
int anInt1411;
int anInt1412;
boolean aBoolean1413;
boolean aBoolean1414;
boolean aBoolean1415;
int anInt1416;
int anInt1417;
int anInt1418;
int anInt1419;
Class19_Sub3 aClass19_Sub3_1420;

}[/code]
See how I made:

Class15 aClass15_1404; Class9 aClass9_1405; Class42 aClass42_1406; Class24 aClass24_1407;
public?

Remember, every deob the numbers will be different, and the Ground won’t always be in Class19_Sub3
